{"tid":1139444,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）wifi 穩定地幾十秒會爆一次ping","createTime":"2019-05-05T09:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T11:54:47.000Z","uid":70753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"24ce8d1da3614f5dca376a767cd4dd7a1731d769","tid":1139444,"uid":70753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"巴打們好，我今年去左台灣交換<br />\n所以自己出黎住<br />\n<br />\n之前都係用電腦插線share wifi，後黎發現個電費好貴，所以死死地氣買左個Router 黎用<br />\nAsus- RT-AC51U (應該好廢，因為平，但見佢至少有雙頻）<br />\n<br />\n但用左幾日發現，個網路平時幾快，但佢平均每幾十分/一分鐘就會爆一次ping<br />\n我上網搵左好多方法，好似改dns,固定wifi channel 都冇得搞<br />\n<br />\n於是就係網上搵左個app幫自己個wifi check 個ping<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sB3z6dk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsB3z6dk.png&h=f5257e01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9hQEym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9hQEym.png&h=77d7848e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CcqboZ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCcqboZ2.png&h=11edfa0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以見到個ping值一直係2-11ms左右 ，其實都夠用。但死就死在我每次check ，過程大概1分鐘，會ping 60次，總有幾次係會由1-11ms 變左90幾-110左右<br />\n我因為係棒球迷成日睇直播，就會發現一分鐘會lag一次咁，但以前用電腦share好似冇呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n我知道個問題可能好蠢，你地鬧我唔緊要，但真係自己搵左好多資料先上黎問<br />\n<br />\n我有搵過包租婆手，但佢又唔識，要搵包租公佢又好似驚死人勾佢老公咁一拖再拖，唔比我直接問佢老公<br />\n<br />\n我係電腦白痴黎，又冇咩朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想搵人幫下手"},{"pid":"d5ca230ffed307668a799e4dd09c1f2d119c0caf","tid":1139444,"uid":37431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"有冇check過QRcO個config?<br />\n將佢換行做331試下"},{"pid":"3e4dd210a360aded0516162ea8b576feff21da2e","tid":1139444,"uid":70753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ca230ffed307668a799e4dd09c1f2d119c0caf","tid":1139444,"uid":37431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"有冇check過QRcO個config?<br />\n將佢換行做331試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:20:27.000Z","msg":"對唔住巴打<br />\n呢個係邊到set架<br />\n我因為電腦白痴黎可唔可以講簡單少少<br />\n<br />\n係咪要開電腦入router setting 果到搞？"},{"pid":"24efc2c1aecc4ec4a4f2a17e4183efbc7d1c6b18","tid":1139444,"uid":70753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ca230ffed307668a799e4dd09c1f2d119c0caf","tid":1139444,"uid":37431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"有冇check過QRcO個config?<br />\n將佢換行做331試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"我上google search QRcO 搵唔到個terms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a25b067d967e9c8b2ead87b8d4c82d1a166d570","tid":1139444,"uid":70753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05ae5b0d313e3a8f33270a304f5792a45bf0dbbd","tid":1139444,"uid":18880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"我屋企用wifi ping又係會咁，但實際用落冇乜野就由佢了"},{"pid":"a78e8d1769fd95efa49b58312623c2425163cafd","tid":1139444,"uid":70753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ae5b0d313e3a8f33270a304f5792a45bf0dbbd","tid":1139444,"uid":18880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"我屋企用wifi ping又係會咁，但實際用落冇乜野就由佢了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"有啊 有時睇波 or陪朋友玩手機game <br />\n會斷一斷 如果係手機game就會每分鐘460一次"},{"pid":"99cdb3aaf8966c869c9815a9b213423470d66994","tid":1139444,"uid":149662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"ohtani 18/5 歸隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1485a18efce66a4b99c9599c4463fe11ce35a779","tid":1139444,"uid":47216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"試下 update router Firmware<br />\n睇吓有冇改善？"},{"pid":"60ffe99845521f9b0b19db88daca5d3fc7706855","tid":1139444,"uid":17032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"